title: Arthur Shawcross - The Genesee River Monster
description:
Hi friends!
 Hope you are having a wonderful day today and I just wanted to say a big thank you to all of you guys who constantly send love my way. I love and appreciate you guys so much!!!
 Anywho, today I wanted to talk about Arthur Shawcross and just, yeah. I mean, what can you say at this point? Gross human. I would love to hear your thoughts down below. Hope you have a great week ahead and I will be seeing you very soon.
x o
Bailey Sarian

P.S. If you haven't already, check out my YouTube @BaileySarian!
